      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, really hits the atmosphere. can you get a bit more specific though? i need to see the people that inhabit this place. like, when you're walking down those streets, what kind of people are you seeing on the corners or hanging out in the doorways that make you feel like you need to keep your head down and move fast? give me some descriptions of the characters that embody that sense of danger and instability.",
